How to build:
  Standard ./configure; make; make install

Dependencies:
  perl
  FFTW >= 3
  BLAS
  LAPACK
  GSL >= 1.9
  Zoltan (internal)
  Spglib (internal)
  Metis (internal/optional)
  Newuoa (internal/optional)
  Qshep (internal/optional)
  Libnbc (internal/optional)
  GD (optional)
  MPI (optional)
  NetCDF (optional)
  Sparskit (optional)
  
Website:
  http://www.tddft.org/programs/octopus/

New releases:
  2009/04/16 Version 3.1

Bugs & Patches:
  http://www.tddft.org/trac/octopus/report

SVN server:
  svn co http://www.tddft.org/svn/octopus/trunk
